definition: Sheyang county in Yancheng 鹽城|盐城[Yan2 cheng2], Jiangsu

sentences.english: Sheyang County is the demonstrative site for Coastal Zone Developmenf of the State Science and Teclmological Commission.
sentences.chinese: 射陽縣是國家科委全國海岸帶開發的示範點。

sentences.english: The equation forecasting the meteorological index has been created with the meteorological data of Sheyang county.
sentences.chinese: 並以射陽縣爲代表建立該氣象指標的預報方程。
